OL,3,CDrivers of bigger cars could be
OL,4,Ccharged more to park in Bristol
OL,6,FDrivers of larger, heavier and more
OL,7,Fpolluting cars could be charged more
OL,8,Fwhen paying to park in Bristol.
OL,10,FPlans are at the "very early stages"
OL,11,Fof being drawn up for a radical change
OL,12,Fin rules, which could also include
OL,13,Freducing the space available for
OL,14,Fparking cars on the side of the road.
