OL,3,CDrivers of bigger cars could be
OL,4,Ccharged more to park in Bristol
OL,6,FTransport bosses at Bristol City
OL,7,FCouncil are being "heavily influenced"
OL,8,Fby Lambeth, where the London borough
OL,9,Fcouncil is planning to turn a quarter
OL,10,Fof space along the side of streets
OL,11,Finto places for trees, benches and
OL,12,Fbicycle storage. Previously, 94% of
OL,13,Fkerbside space was for parking.
OL,15,FLambeth bases the cost of a residents'
OL,16,Fparking permit based on the carbon
OL,17,Fdioxide emissions of their vehicle.
OL,18,FCouncillors on the transport policy
OL,19,Fcommittee will vote on 24 October on
OL,20,Festablishing a group to explore all
OL,21,Fthe options.
