OL,6,FA committee report said: "The project
OL,7,Fwill include outlining our strategy
OL,8,Ffor managing on-street, off-street and
OL,9,Fresident parking scheme parking,
OL,10,Fincluding pricing strategy, demand
OL,11,Fmanagement and variations on pricing
OL,12,Fcategories, e.g. weight, emissions and
OL,13,Fsize-based pricing.
