OL,3,CDrivers of bigger cars could be
OL,4,Ccharged more to park in Bristol
OL,6,F"The kerbside is currently dominated
OL,7,Fby parking and parking-related
OL,8,Finfrastructure and restrictions, which
OL,9,Fis out of step with corporate policies
OL,10,Fand a highly inefficient use of land.
OL,11,FReallocating space away from parking
OL,12,Fto other modes of transport will
OL,13,Fensure residents and visitors to
OL,14,FBristol have more choice and can make
OL,15,Fthe switch from private vehicles."
