OL,3,CDrivers of bigger cars could be
OL,4,Ccharged more to park in Bristol
OL,6,FLarger cars, such as SUVs, have become
OL,7,Fmore popular in Britain in recent
OL,8,Fyears, taking up more space on
OL,9,Fcongested city streets and emitting
OL,10,Fmore carbon dioxide. Other European
OL,11,Fcities have also recently rolled out
OL,12,Fextra parking charges for larger cars,
OL,13,Fsuch as Paris and Bath.
