OL,3,CDrivers of bigger cars could be
OL,4,Ccharged more to park in Bristol
OL,6,FThe new task group will also explore a
OL,7,F"gradual reallocation of (kerbside)
OL,8,Fspace to sustainable modes of
OL,9,Ftransport and alternative uses, e.g.
OL,10,Ftree planting, SUDs (sustainable
OL,11,Fdrainage systems), cycle hangars and
OL,12,Fseating". Councillors previously
OL,13,Fmentioned a potential ban on pavement
OL,14,Fparking, which could be rolled out in
OL,15,Fcertain parts of the city.
