OL,6,FThe task group will likely meet online
OL,7,Fin private for about an hour every
OL,8,Fmonth, and the project is expected to
OL,9,Ftake one year to develop. The council
OL,10,Fwould then consult the public on any
OL,11,Fproposed changes to parking rules,
OL,12,Fbefore the transport committee takes
OL,13,Fthe final decision.
